Basically when our pets are on a mob, we are placed on their hate list in some way or form.  This is why when our pets die the mobs will come after us.  Consequently, if you send your pet to take a DT from a mob (this used to work long ago), you yourself will get nailed and die from that first DT (not the pet).   <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=222062">Booperbustle Tinkermeister</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
